article.headline: Crews scores 20 in UT Martin's 80-74 victory against Eastern Kentucky

images.name: UT Martin Skyhawks vs. Eastern Kentucky Colonels: Full Highlights
images.caption: UT Martin Skyhawks vs. Eastern Kentucky Colonels: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Crews scores 20 in UT Martin's 80-74 victory against Eastern Kentucky
article.story: RICHMOND, Ky. -- — Jacob Crews' 20 points helped UT Martin defeat Eastern Kentucky 80-74 on Friday night. Crews added nine rebounds for the Skyhawks (3-1). Jordan Sears scored 18 points, going 8 of 12 from the field. Issa Muhammad shot 7 of 10 from the field to finish with 14 points. The Colonels (2-1) were led by Leland Walker, who posted 21 points. Isaiah Cozart added 13 points, six rebounds and three blocks for Eastern Kentucky. In addition, Devontae Blanton had 12 points, six rebounds, four assists, two steals and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
